Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你要睡到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:32.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚才睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:37.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忙什么啊忙到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:40.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我制作了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:55.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是....什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:59.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:05.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我睡会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:08.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:09.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快起床...

Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:56.71,FBT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}通向黎明的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:34.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是谁害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:42.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买个午饭连人影都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得买了面包回教室太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得屋顶才更远...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 从哪看不都是一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:24.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想她拿着便当去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱绘你声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢 那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是到底在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:39.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 公园的附近有艘很大船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:43.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的港口每次都会有别样的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个拍照的好地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个马上就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条河边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:56.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上大桥旁的台阶 就能把整个城市一览无余了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:05:00.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天放晴的时候那儿的景色真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:01.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:02.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:06.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天探望姐姐的时候 你能先去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送去修的照相机修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得去店里拿才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事什么时候去不都行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:20.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 邂逅不知道在何时何地就会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指和天空的邂逅?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会有其他的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉真名 办完事后我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:34.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又这么说 上次不也没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一点也没改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说真名被甩了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空什么的 我最~讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:45.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:57.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:13.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森宫君被真名告白后一定觉得很不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:16.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以午休以后就翘课了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:19.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 行了 虽然不知道你又在妄想什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:24.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近你们2个在一起的时间变多了这是个不争的事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连塔子也是 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是去同一家医院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常在一起也无可厚非嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去医院了 先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再聊一次比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森宫君很喜欢天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:49.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起草莓样式的 星星和云样式效果会更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 又说这些莫名其妙的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没弄明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是迟钝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱绘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:10.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的给我看!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 让我看!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:22.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都怪纱绘要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:49.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我这就把小依带回病房去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我想他一会就来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小依这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀

Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:57.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃鱼子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是个难题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 看来没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名 抱歉 我马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然没发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病时间早就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:43.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 明天一定要好好和苍乃道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真难办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:49.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:45.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 从哪开始找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明把钱放进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼...好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1...2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:30.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:34.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你用头一下子钻进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:40.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点红肿已经很庆幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过想吃鱼子酱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼子酱 鲑鱼子不都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃倒是吃的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是想吃鹅肝酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹅肝酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去买
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:05.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不吃了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 公主很不高兴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是长途旅行有点累了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找个地方藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.36,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:26.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了鹅肝酱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我的那份都拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:04.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天是苍乃的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:08.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想带到医院去 怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话姐姐会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:15.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那么接下来我们去商店选购吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来? 不是明天去?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 必须得事先预订才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:28.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一定要预订的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:38.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会说今天也有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我一定会去医院的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:41.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:45.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我要利用之前的时间...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等等 真名小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:54.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近生日蛋糕的种类很多我们得多花点时间认真选
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够呛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:18.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新型的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:25.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到要预订蛋糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日蛋糕嘛 这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:32.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许选个小点的不更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:35.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的话就只能插几根蜡烛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备插几根啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天真是另人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍乃姐的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:54.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小依在自己生日前一天总是紧张的睡不着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小依是不是有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深信那样才算是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:10.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:18.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你要到什么时候才能叫对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.42,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:23.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直适应不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 身体...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:34.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 昨天...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 虽然有点那个 今天特地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:40.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 是双胞胎人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:47.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人眨眼的地方很吸引人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:48.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:50.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是姐姐的生日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备了秘密的礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.88,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:04.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依人的「没问题」啦「当然」啦这些完全没有说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...

Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不就是说谎了吗

Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.26,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次绝对不会了

Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽说谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天真是值得期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍乃也说说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和姐姐没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:22.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次也是明明是上课却不在教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在屋顶上拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:27.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:31.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来小依不是站在我这边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么小依要站在你那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是依人不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:39.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:45.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不讨厌依人拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:52.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 下次我把照片也带来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样的话 最好是黎明的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了姐姐我会鼓足干劲带一张很美的照片来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:06.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的人偶看起来姐姐好象也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:31.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:54.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:21.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:34.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为还有不少的呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:51.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我这个谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:04.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是四方茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住所是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?住所?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:14.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 住所就写教会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:30.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 味道好象有点不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:35.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 之后去哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:37.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:18.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:32.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才这么早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:43.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:19.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1...2...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:22.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:26.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----以下为sola Prelude出现过的插曲内容----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さらわれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと　そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えてもかまわないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ　残る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气持ちはどこかへ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ　いろを落とすでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも　时は同じ思いだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ　描きつづければ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁も 知らず
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日が射すまでに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと　そっと

